.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-HTLC-TIMEOUT-MAX" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-htlc-timeout-max \- FEAT-2502 channel with highest HTLC expiry (cltv_expiry) among all HTLCs
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-htlc-timeout-max
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-htlc-timeout-max for lightning CLI (FEAT-2502).
.PP
Returns the channel ID and maximum cltv_expiry value across all pending HTLCs.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
